name: Paskong Pilipino 2021 - A Christmas Contest Entry
description:
A Filipino Christmas in 2021. A nostalgic homage to cartoonist Larry Alcala's Slice of Life illustration. It's an alternative look at Christmas 2021 in the city; "alternative" because only one person is wearing a mask. Can you find him/her? 

Look also for:
1. Jesus
2. 2 cats, 2 dogs, and 2 pigs
3. 3 crypto logos
